## Market Segmentation
* What product type will be targeted the most for installations? Decorative fans are expected to be selling rapidly owing to rising value towards aesthetics and interior design.
* Which fan size will be focused on the most regarding sales? Medium-sized fans are expected to dominate due to their ability to balance space and air circulation.
* Which application is expected to benefit the most from revenue generation? Residential fans are expected to be highly accommodating due to rising installations in bedrooms.
* Which distribution channel is expected to generate the most value for the market? Offline channels are expected to dispense most products due to easy availability.